      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Board and General Meeting Minutes <unitdate type="inclusive" normal="1933/1990">1933-1990</unitdate></unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Minutes of the Board and General Meetings document the activities of the Thrift Shop Association for almost each month with the exception of 1978 and 1979 which have not been received (there are minutes from one meeting each for each of the two years). The board and general meeting minutes have been filed together or separately for each year, depending on how they were received. (It is also important to note that the Thrift Shop Association made a transition from an April to April fiscal year to a January to December fiscal year in 1958.)</p>
        </scopecontent>
