      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Committee Records <unitdate type="inclusive" normal="1930/1989" certainty="approximate">1930s-1980s (scattered dates)</unitdate></unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>Although the Board and General Meeting Minutes document the activities of the Association's committees, the series of Committee files also detail their activities. The committee files have been organized alphabetically by committee name, and each committee has at least an annual report of all activities. Of particular interest because its activities have been documented in the greatest detail is the Social Service Committee. This committee, more than the others, was concerned with the specific relief efforts of the Association.</p>
        </scopecontent>
